{
  "name": "android-debugger",
  "version": "1.2.1",
  "description": "Drive an Android app debugging session from Claude Code — set/conditional breakpoints, watches, step over/into/out, evaluate expressions, inspect frames and locals. Backed by a Kotlin MCP server using JDI (Java Debug Interface) over JDWP via adb forward. Cross-platform: macOS, Linux, Windows.",
